Trade/Device Name(s): TD-4140 Smart Dongle Blood Glucose plus β-ketone Monitoring System
Method(s)/Technology(ies): Enzyme assay (Glucose Dehydrogenase for glucose, β-hydroxybutyrate dehydrogenase for ketone)
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for TaiDoc TD-4140 Smart Dongle Blood Glucose plus β-ketone Monitoring System for quantitative measurement of glucose and β-ketone in capillary whole blood using electrochemical biosensor technology
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for quantitative measurement of glucose and β-ketone in fresh capillary whole blood from the finger for self-testing by people with diabetes at home to monitor effectiveness of diabetes control; not for diagnosis or screening of diabetes, nor for use on neonates
